:0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"We are temporarily using live channel直播台as english channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634498\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634498</a>"},{"pid":"1934815ce1fd63c72b44fe72e0d60684a8762db2","tid":1634540,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:35:29.000Z","msg":"瞄腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64037f3459e6a990177758fecd05a86a0d56c63","tid":1634540,"uid":225567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:37:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9756565ad9f8a40fa06cf04fbc389b6eb3259eb","tid":1634540,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:37:28.000Z","msg":"瞄腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd462ee6f204956585753e84a093c1d74472e7a6","tid":1634540,"uid":280347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"打下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有藍絲美容院老闆試圖高空擲物謀殺手足！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634619</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9d37952cf24b031590fda7c00216a9e5ffd5cab","tid":1634540,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"喵腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1094629e1c0f49b994fc19595ca92283ecb941d4","tid":1634540,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774cb233fd7fc8b979cdf46764c7089eb4fb6e5b","tid":1634540,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次開po，因為個人真係唔鍾意開po，唔好當我係鬼。<br />\n<br />\n有見琴日打機有殺人既機械兵成功撞到我地絲打終身殘廢，現場有好多左膠都阻止左神獸繼續打機械兵司機，事後相信好多支持神獸既手足覺得阻膠有份害，令敵人下次一定更踴躍用車撞手足，並覺得下次一定會打埋阻膠，包括我自己都咁認為。而另一邊左膠或自稱和理非既左膠亦覺得當時現場既阻膠手足係決定得明確同表現理智，否則神獸有可能殺死隻怪令手足陷入被告謀殺既險境，國際戰線亦更難打。<br />\n<br />\n本人對哩件事相當憤怒，但沉思一晚覺得我地都係唔應該分化，亦唔應該同阻膠割蓆。有見及此，我諗左條絕世好橋令阻膠同神獸和解，就係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試著不要說「唔好打！」，而係要說「瞄腳！」</span><br />\n<br />\n因為神獸未完全成為究極體，只係得打頭既技能，而常識都知打頭係唔會令人殘廢，只會令人死。而連登係好早721已經吹風話見黑社會應該打膝蓋，但遲遲未見有人做。哩個時候左膠就可以成為神獸既增幅器，幫神獸指向殺人犯既腳部集中攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n我地都知打腳係唔令人死，而且仲可以令犯人永久殘廢，不但可以令犯人再冇能力出黎恐襲手足，仲有強大阻嚇作用。而因為今次已經有絲打犧牲對腳，我地瞄恐怖分子既腳打亦係出師有名，係國際畫面係有光環。<br />\n<br />\n如果認同既話，就跟我一齊講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">瞄腳！</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eea71e56d03c30b80ebed85e70712ecf77ad243","tid":1634540,"uid":159113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"瞄膝頭 一對腳"},{"pid":"1a681c2054a226574d1945a51573115e067f0355","tid":1634540,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:53:05.000Z","msg":"瞄腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b891715d45566b52de2149e0ddf888af9ac8cbb4","tid":1634540,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"腳呀！腳呀！<br />\n<br />\n會唔會順口啲"},{"pid":"6f655a03b66f02d08f7a9a50845bd7c6167b21ed","tid":1634540,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48cc88ef38c843b112f16fc91b11f568c0b39303","tid":1634540,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:32:04.000Z","msg":"全民㩒爆atm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:01:53.000Z","msg":"撳爆atm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ded47e2d622ea6624cc59fcba01686801dda18c","tid":1634540,"uid":238500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20